{
  "title": "Working with Content",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Working with Content</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\"> Information on using art created in external applications, importing it into Unreal Engine, and setting it up for use in visualization and interactive applications. </p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Working with Content\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/87a57669-78b5-47f2-9723-3bfd93050588?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/87a57669-78b5-47f2-9723-3bfd93050588?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/87a57669-78b5-47f2-9723-3bfd93050588?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"13\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"12\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Most of the artistic assets that you will use in Unreal Engine are created using external 3D applications, such as 3ds Max, Maya, Quixel, ZBrush, and others. Below, you will find information on the types of assets that are created externally and what tools are available for bringing them into the engine.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table\" style=\"--columns-count: 2;\"><!----><!----><thead><tr><th> Asset Creation Locations </th><th> &nbsp; </th><!----></tr><tr><th> Created in Unreal Editor </th><th> Created Using External Application </th><!----></tr><!----></thead><!----><!----><!----><!----><tbody><tr><td><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><ul><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Game Levels</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Materials</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Particle Systems</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Cinematic Sequences</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Blueprint Scripts</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">AI Navigation Meshes</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Precalculated Light Maps</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Level Lights</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><!----><!----></ul><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></td><td><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><ul><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Static Meshes</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Skeletal Meshes</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Skeletal Animation</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Textures</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Sounds (WAVs)</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">IES Light Profiles</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li><li><!----><!----><!----><!-